{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be vibrant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EdTech Platform</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff;\n            --secondary-color: #e6f2ff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.7), rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/007bff/ffffff?text=EdTech+Hero') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            position: relative;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.5); /* Overlay for better text readability */\n        }\n\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #features {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>EduFuture</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Unlock Your Potential</h2>\n            <p>Learn, grow, and achieve your goals with our innovative edtech solutions.</p>\n            <a href=\"#features\" class=\"btn\">Explore Courses</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-book-open\"></i>\n                    <h3>Interactive Lessons</h3>\n                    <p>Engage with dynamic content designed for effective learning.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Personalized Paths</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored learning journeys to suit your pace and style.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                    <h3>Expert Instructors</h3>\n                    <p>Learn from industry professionals and passionate educators.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-award\"></i>\n                    <h3>Certifications</h3>\n                    <p>Earn recognized credentials upon course completion.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 EduFuture. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}